              double latitude,

        Class constructor with parameters
        Parameters:
        id - An int value that represents the id of the Coupon, also the primary key of the object
        business - A string that represents the business that issued the coupon
        image - A string that represents the url of the image on the ftp storage server
        details - A string the defines additional details about the coupon
        category - A string that represents the category of products the coupon is related to
        date - A Date object that represents the timestamp of the expiry date of the coupon (date + time)
        latitude - A double value that represents the latitude coordinate of the coupon
        longitude - A double value that represents the longitude coordinate of the coupon
